         LOG_PRINT_L1("We sent that one");
       }
     }
-    else
-    {
-      LOG_PRINT_L1("Already saw that one, it's for us");
-      txids.push_back({txid, true});
-    }
   }

   // get those txes

```

Further patch to simplewallet, which will replace 6413d601606a9642fa8b60c00823364abb7ffc83.
Note that the delays must be randomized, since you can't refresh while a password prompt is being displayed.
Allowing this would require non trivial changes to the wallet refresh code.
With this patch, the wallet will refresh on an integer number of seconds after last time, but the number of seconds is randomized within an appropriate range.

